The Easee One has been making waves in the UK EV charging market — and one look at it tells you why. This Norwegian-designed charger is genuinely one of the best-looking units you can bolt to a wall. But a pretty face only gets you so far. The real question is whether the Easee Charge app and smart features can keep up with rivals like the [Ohme Home Pro](/reviews/ohme-home-pro-review/) and [myenergi Zappi](/reviews/zappi-v2-review/).

We've spent time with the Easee One to give you the full picture.

